      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:15:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meme-Stock 投资者因美国能源公司收购案损失数百万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/meme-stock-traders-lament-tellurian-tell-deal-after-losing-millions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于过去几年大举投资美国能源公司 Tellurian Inc. 的 Bjorn Bos 和其他散户投资者来说，事情本不应该以这种方式结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/meme-stock-traders-lament-tellurian-tell-deal-after-losing-millions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:08:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>二叠纪生产商 Matador 上调 2024 年石油产量计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/permian-producer-matador-increases-2024-oil-output-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Matador Resources Co. 计划在 2024 年产出比原先预期更多的石油，这表明二叠纪盆地西部的油井（美国产量最高的油田）将给钻井者带来意外的收益，并增强全国石油供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/permian-producer-matador-increases-2024-oil-output-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:59:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>页岩老板警告称，禁止水力压裂会导致天然气价格“暴涨”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/banning-fracking-would-threaten-eqt-s-output-by-25-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果禁止水力压裂，天然气价格将“飙升”。页岩钻探公司 EQT Corp. 的首席执行官托比·赖斯 (Toby Rice) 表示，在总统乔·拜登 (Joe Biden) 表示将退出竞选后，他是化石燃料行业首批对选举发表评论的知名人士之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/banning-fracking-would-threaten-eqt-s-output-by-25-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:50:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杜德利加剧美联储降息猜测，美国国债收益率下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/treasury-yields-slide-as-weak-data-bolster-bets-on-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测美联储官员将很快下调美国利率，两年期美国国债收益率跌至二月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/treasury-yields-slide-as-weak-data-bolster-bets-on-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
